org.apache.flink.runtime.fs.s3

Class S3BucketObjectPair

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.fs.s3.S3BucketObjectPair

  • public final class S3BucketObjectPair
extends Object
    An S3 bucket-object pair identifies either a bucket in S3 or an object. If the object property is null, this object identifies an S3 bucket. If both the bucket and the object property is null, the object refers to the S3 base directory.

    This class is thread-safe.
